liam-f-buckley-jr">William F. Buckley, Jr.</a>, <a href="/characters/1041313-hillary-clinton">Hillary Clinton</a><span class="toggleLink"><a hide_txt="...less" class="actionLinkLite hideLink" tag="span" href="#" onclick="$j(&#39;#more95&#39;).hide(); $j(&#39;#more_show95&#39;).show();; return false;">...less</a></span></span>
